== BIOS Password ==

{{mbox
| type      = notice
| image   = [[File:Ambox_notice.png|40px|alt=Info]]
| text       = The instructions in this section refer to BIOS or legacy BIOS. Users with UEFI firware should research specific instructions for their computer.
